<subSubSection box="[199,1369,1475,1502]" pageId="27" pageNumber="214" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="27.[151,1437,827,1538]" box="[199,1369,1475,1502]" pageId="27" pageNumber="214">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1476,1502]" pageId="27" pageNumber="214">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named after the pair of processes on ventral margin of each superior process of genital cup.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
